org.webchecker.forms

Class CheckboxInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.webchecker.forms.Input
      • org.webchecker.forms.CheckboxInput

  • public class CheckboxInput
extends Input
    HTML form input element with type checkbox. Extends from Input, but differs itself by considering also default value of input element.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jindřich Máca (Tuník)
